These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: sudoku, filmmaking, traveling, writing
Game: whist, mah-jongg, scrabble, go
Transport: trike, airplane, roller, helicopter
Job: manager, teacher, project-manager, firefighter
 1. Game:whist is on the right of Game:mah-jongg##1
 2. Hobby:sudoku is in an even position##4
 3. Transport:trike is on the left of Game:scrabble##1
 4. Transport:roller is on the right of Hobby:writing##1
 5. Game:whist is on the left or right of Game:mah-jongg##3
 6. Job:manager is on the left of Hobby:filmmaking##1
 7. Transport:airplane == Hobby:traveling##1
 8. Job:project-manager is in an even position##4
 9. Job:manager is between Job:firefighter and Game:go##2
10. Hobby:sudoku == Job:firefighter##1
11. Game:scrabble == Hobby:writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Hobby          | traveling  | sudoku    | writing    | filmmaking   |
| Game   | mah-jongg     | whist   | scrabble       | go    |
| Transport   | airplane | trike | helicopter    | roller |
| Job           | teacher | firefighter       | manager | project-manager     |

