 8. Beverage:lemonade is on the left or right of Color:white##3
 9. Beverage:almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
10. Cigar:bolivar is in an odd position##4
11. Beverage:almond-milk == Flower:dahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
